INSERT INTO featureI18n VALUES('LMEjvwaAsa5P','en','Chung Kee Modern Fashion',0,replace('This fantastic Modernist Tong4 lau4*2 (唐樓 vernacular tenement building) at 160 Third Street in Sai Ying Pun has two especially great features: an oculus (A small window, in a dome or a wall that is circular or oval in shape) and a Ghost Sign!\n\nIt looks like the space is used for storage now but once upon a time it was 松記 (cung4 gei3) which announced itself with the tagline, "大新時裝" (daai6 san1 si4 zong1 ''Big New Fashion''). Perhaps it was a trendy boutique?\n\nLong before it was fashionable, Sai Ying Pun was home to many brothels and even the Bubonic Plague (just like neighbouring Tai Ping Shan). That was in the late 1800s and this building was completed in 1950 so it came long after that. The neighbourhood must have seen some interesting times, though, as it was also once home to the Berlin Foundling House, a Sailors Home, and a Lunatic Asylum.\n\nSometimes Ghost Signs simply scratch the surface of the fascinating history of a neighbourhood...','\n',char(10)),0,'160 Third St, Sai Wan',1,'{"buildingNumberFrom":"160","streetName":"Third Street","neighbourhood":"Sai Wan","district":null,"region":"HK","country":"HKSAR"}');
INSERT INTO featureI18n VALUES('LMEjvwaAsa5P','zh-hant','Chung Kee現代時裝',1,replace('位於西營盤第三街160號嘅現代主義唐樓4 lau4*2 （唐樓鄉土唐樓）有兩個特別正嘅特點：眼孔（圓頂或圓形牆壁上嘅細窗）同鬼招牌！\n\n而家睇嚟呢個空間係用嚟存放嘅，但曾幾何時係松記（ cung4 gei3 ）以“大新時尚”（ daai6 san1 si4 zong1 '' Big New Fashion''）嘅標語嚟宣佈自己。 或者係一家時尚嘅精品店？\n\n早在它流行之前，西營盤就是許多妓院甚至腺鼠疫的所在地（就像鄰近的太平山一樣）。 係喺1800年代後期，座建築於1950年完工，所以係喺之後好耐先建成嘅。 不過，呢個街區一定經歷過一些有趣嘅時光，因為它都曾經係柏林育嬰堂、水手之家同疯人院嘅所在地。\n\n有時，幽靈標誌只係觸及咗一個社區迷人歷史嘅表面......','\n',char(10)),1,'第三街160號中西區',1,'{"buildingNumberFrom":"160","streetName":"第三街","neighbourhood":"西環","district":"中西區","region":null,"country":"香港特區"}');
INSERT INTO featureI18n VALUES('LMEjvwaAsa5P','zh-hans','Chung Kee 现代时装',1,replace('位于西营盘第三街 160 号的现代主义唐楼4 lau4*2 （唐樓 乡土唐楼） 有两个特别棒的特点：眼孔（圆顶或圆形墙壁上的小窗户）和鬼招牌！\n\n现在看起来这个空间是用来存放的，但曾几何时是松記 （cung4 gei3） 以 “大新时尚” （daai6 san1 si4 zong1 ''Big New Fashion''） 的标语来宣布自己。也许这是一家时尚的精品店？\n\n早在它流行之前，西营盘就是许多妓院甚至腺鼠疫的所在地（就像邻近的太平山一样）。那是在 1800 年代后期，这座建筑于 1950 年完工，所以是在那之后很久才建成的。不过，这个街区一定经历过一些有趣的时光，因为它也曾经是柏林育婴堂、水手之家和疯人院的所在地。\n\n有时，幽灵标志只是触及了一个社区迷人历史的表面......','\n',char(10)),1,'第三街160号中西区',1,'{"buildingNumberFrom":"160","streetName":"第三街","neighbourhood":"西环","district":"中西区","region":null,"country":"香港特区"}');
