INSERT INTO featureI18n VALUES('zbM9wNSjXmIc','en','''Kam Lan Tea & Tobacco''',0,replace('Shophouses were once common in Hong Kong but they’re becoming rarer these days. Luckily this row of shophouses in Mong Kok has been partially preserved along with its many Ghost Signs.\n\nAt 618 Shanghai Street you’ll see all sorts of defunct signage for leather wares and shoes, floor tiles, handrails and much more. These ones are signs for 錦蘭茶煙莊(cigarettes and tea), 華生電器行(plumbing and electrical services) and others.\n\nThis cluster of ten shophouses between 600 and 626 Shanghai Street escaped the wrecking ball by pure luck - by 2008 it was the largest collection of shophouses in the city. That year they were acquired by the Urban Renewal Authority, which pledged to restore them; however only the facades remain. The inside is an entirely new building. \n\nStill, we have the Ghost Signs to enjoy and the development does have augmented reality that tells you more about the buildings’ signage. \n\nTake a look when you’re next in Mong Kok!','\n',char(10)),0,'33 A Argyle St, Mong Kok',1,'{"buildingName":"Memoir Center","buildingNumberFrom":"33A","streetName":"Argyle Street","neighbourhood":"Mong Kok","district":"YTM","region":"KL","country":"HKSAR"}');
INSERT INTO featureI18n VALUES('zbM9wNSjXmIc','zh-hant','''Kam Lan Tea & Tobacco''',1,replace('店屋喺香港曾經好常見，但如今越嚟越少見。 幸運嘅係，旺角嘅排店屋及其好多鬼標誌已被部分保存落嚟。\n\n在上海街618號，你會看到各種已停業嘅皮具和鞋子、地磚、扶手等標牌。 呢啲標誌係香煙和茶、水暖和電力服務等嘅標誌。\n\n群位於上海街600至626號之間嘅10間店屋完全靠運氣逃脫了這場災難——到2008年，它已成為該市最大嘅店屋集合。 一年，它們被市區重建局收購，並承諾修復它們; 然而，只剩外牆。 內部係一座全新嘅建築。 \n\n儘琯如此，我哋都係有Ghost Signs可以享受，而且開發項目確實具有增強現實功能，可以話畀你更多關於建築物標牌嘅信息。 \n\n快啲嚟睇吓你下次來到旺角嘅時候啦！','\n',char(10)),1,'民華中心亞皆老街33A號油尖旺區',1,'{"buildingName":"民華中心","buildingNumberFrom":"33A","streetName":"亞皆老街","neighbourhood":"旺角","district":"油尖旺區","region":"九龍","country":"香港特區"}');
INSERT INTO featureI18n VALUES('zbM9wNSjXmIc','zh-hans','''Kam Lan Tea & Tobacco''',1,replace('店屋在香港曾经很常见，但如今越来越少见。幸运的是，旺角的这一排店屋及其许多鬼标志已被部分保存下来。\n\n在上海街 618 号，您会看到各种已停业的皮具和鞋子、地砖、扶手等标牌。这些标志是香烟和茶、水暖和电力服务等的标志。\n\n这群位于上海街 600 至 626 号之间的 10 间店屋完全靠运气逃脱了这场灾难——到 2008 年，它已成为该市最大的店屋集合。那一年，它们被市区重建局收购，并承诺修复它们;然而，只剩下外墙。内部是一座全新的建筑。\n\n尽管如此，我们还是有 Ghost Signs 可以享受，而且开发项目确实具有增强现实功能，可以告诉您更多关于建筑物标牌的信息。\n\n快来看看您下次来到旺角的时候吧！','\n',char(10)),1,'民华中心亚皆老街33A号油尖旺区',1,'{"buildingName":"民华中心","buildingNumberFrom":"33A","streetName":"亚皆老街","neighbourhood":"旺角","district":"油尖旺区","region":"九龙","country":"香港特区"}');
