INSERT INTO featureI18n VALUES('SZtdR8sCkV_Y','en','Unique Tower Sales Office',0,replace('A Ghost Sign emerges amidst the economic ebb & flow of a neighbourhood.\n\nBut, for something so temporary, this Ghost Sign for the Unique Tower Sales Office 旭逸閣洽購處 (juk1 jat6 gok3 hap1 kau3 cyu3) is beautiful and elaborate!\n\nRight across the road from the Happy Valley Race Course, this Ghost Sign would have been painted around 1982 when the building was completed. You can tell it''s quite an old sign based on how it''s written right to left rather than left to right.\n\nAs soon as the units were sold, though, this hand-painted marvel would have been covered up.\n\nFor many years this space was occupied by Chuk Yuen Seafood Restaurant, which placed a massive sign board and shop front over the sales office sign complete with an iconic lobster shaped neon (see the Google Maps screenshot for what it looked like).\n\nSadly, like so many other restaurants, Chuk Yuen had to move during the pandemic. Another piece of the old neighborhood gone. When the neon came down, this Ghost Sign was revealed for a brief moment, only to be replaced by a Kai Bo frozen seafood market.\n\nPerhaps we''ll see this beautiful sign again someday...if only temporarily.','\n',char(10)),0,'7 Wong Nai Chung Rd, Happy Valley',1,'{"buildingNumberFrom":"7","buildingNumberTo":"9","streetName":"Wong Nai Chung Road","neighbourhood":"Happy Valley","district":"WC","region":"HK","country":"HKSAR"}');
INSERT INTO featureI18n VALUES('SZtdR8sCkV_Y','zh-hant','Unique Tower銷售處',1,replace('一個幽靈標誌出現喺一個社區嘅經濟起伏中。\n\n但是，對於如此短暫嘅嘢，呢個Unique Tower Sales Office嘅幽靈標誌（ juk1 jat6 gok3 hap1 kau3 cyu3 ）既美麗又精緻！\n\n就喺跑馬地馬場嘅馬路對面，呢個鬼標誌應該係喺1982年左右完成時繪製嘅。 你可以根據佢係由右到左而唔係由左到右嘅書寫方式嚟判斷係一個相當古老嘅標誌。\n\n然而，一旦呢啲設備售出，呢個手繪奇蹟就會被掩蓋。\n\n多年來，這個空間一直被竹園海鮮餐廳佔據，它在售樓處招牌上方放置了一個巨大的招牌和店面，並配有標誌性的龍蝦形霓虹燈（請參閱谷歌地圖屏幕截圖了解其外觀）。\n\n可惜嘅係，與許多其他餐廳一樣，竹園喺大流行期間不得不搬遷。 老街區嘅另一部分消失了。 当霓虹燈落下時，呢個鬼星座短暫地顯現出嚟，取而代之嘅係凯博冷凍海鮮市場。\n\n或者有一日我哋會再次睇到呢個靚嘅標誌...... 即使只係暫時嘅。','\n',char(10)),1,'黃泥涌道7號灣仔區',1,'{"buildingNumberFrom":"7","buildingNumberTo":"9","streetName":"黃泥涌道","neighbourhood":"跑馬地","district":"灣仔區","region":null,"country":"香港特區"}');
INSERT INTO featureI18n VALUES('SZtdR8sCkV_Y','zh-hans','Unique Tower 销售处',1,replace('一个幽灵标志出现在一个社区的经济起伏中。\n\n但是，对于如此短暂的东西，这个 Unique Tower Sales Office 的幽灵标志 （juk1 jat6 gok3 hap1 kau3 cyu3） 既美丽又精致！\n\n就在跑马地马场的马路对面，这个鬼标志应该是在 1982 年左右完成时绘制的。你可以根据它是从右到左而不是从左到右的书写方式来判断这是一个相当古老的标志。\n\n然而，一旦这些设备售出，这个手绘奇迹就会被掩盖。\n\n多年来，这个空间一直被竹园海鲜餐厅占据，它在售楼处招牌上方放置了一个巨大的招牌和店面，并配有标志性的龙虾形霓虹灯（请参阅谷歌地图屏幕截图了解其外观）。\n\n遗憾的是，与许多其他餐厅一样，竹园在大流行期间不得不搬迁。老街区的另一部分消失了。当霓虹灯落下时，这个鬼星座短暂地显现出来，取而代之的是凯博冷冻海鲜市场。\n\n也许有一天我们会再次看到这个美丽的标志......即使只是暂时的。','\n',char(10)),1,'黄泥涌道7号湾仔区',1,'{"buildingNumberFrom":"7","buildingNumberTo":"9","streetName":"黄泥涌道","neighbourhood":"跑马地","district":"湾仔区","region":null,"country":"香港特区"}');
